title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 11 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 11 2021
description:
In the third hour, C&B are joined by Salena Zito, a reporter for The Washington Examiner, a columnist for the New York Post and Pittsburgh Post-Gazette and author of "The Great Revolt." Listen as she breaks down Biden's unpopularity in the polls and what this could mean in upcoming elections. Double vaccinated Jen Psaki is back at the podium after recovering from covid. Does "Let's Go, Brandon!" chant bother the Biden White House? What's your favorite bumper music? It's impressive the amount of things Biden has wrecked.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
